At the Centre for Entrepreneurship Development (CED), Anna University, our vision is to ignite the spirit of innovation and entrepreneurship among students, faculty, and aspiring innovators across Tamil Nadu. <br/><br/>

We believe that entrepreneurship is not just about starting businesses—it’s about building solutions, solving problems, and shaping a better future.<br/><br/>

Our mission is to provide the right environment, mentorship, infrastructure, and exposure that enable young minds to transform ideas into impactful ventures.<br/><br/>

CED acts as a catalyst, connecting academia, industry, and government, to foster a dynamic and inclusive startup ecosystem.<br/><br/>

We empower students through hands-on training, bootcamps, internships, hackathons, innovation competitions, and funding opportunities.<br/><br/>

We proudly collaborate with institutions, startups, NGOs, and government agencies to ensure our programs are relevant, accessible, and scalable.<br/><br/>

Our initiatives have reached every corner of the state—from rural innovators to emerging techpreneurs—bridging gaps and building capacity.<br/><br/>

We strongly believe that entrepreneurship can drive social change, create employment, and contribute to national growth.<br/><br/>

At CED, we support innovators from ideation to acceleration, and from research labs to real-world impact.<br/><br/>

We encourage interdisciplinary thinking, resilience, and the courage to take risks.<br/><br/>

Our vibrant student communities, like Startify and Innotheon, are nurturing tomorrow’s changemakers.<br/><br/>

We are constantly evolving—embracing new technologies like AI, IoT, AR/VR, and sustainability-driven solutions.<br/><br/>

Every program we design is rooted in inclusion, empowerment, and excellence.<br/><br/>

We invite students, researchers, startups, mentors, and institutions to join hands with us.<br/><br/>

Together, let’s create a culture where innovation thrives and entrepreneurship leads.<br/><br/>

We welcome you to be a part of our journey in shaping the future.<br/><br/>

Visit our initiatives, engage with our programs, and take your first step toward impactful innovation.<br/><br/>

Let CED be your launchpad toward purpose-driven success.

